A vintage-style illustrated career roadmap rendered as an intricate hand-drawn treasure map on aged parchment paper, showing interconnected circular islands floating in a sepia-toned ocean. Each island represents a different skill domain - one covered in mechanical gears and cogs, another with miniature server towers growing like trees, a third with flowing rivers of connected nodes, and others featuring abstract symbols of logic puzzles and architectural blueprints. Dotted pathways wind between the islands like trade routes, with small sailing ships navigating the waters. The map has ornate compass roses, decorative cartouche borders with flourishes, and weathered edges with coffee stains. Warm amber and brown tones dominate with touches of faded navy blue ink. The perspective is top-down, as if viewing an explorer's desk with the map slightly curled at corners.
